7:T54b,Tracy is soul guide and mentor, energetic interpreter, and international facilitator based on the Kohala Coast. She is given to empowering souls deeply landed in matter and honoring the multitude of realities and expressions of love within each of us. Tracy has spent the last decade immersed in both study and practice within traditions of healing and integration, energetic mastery, and soul initiation. She combines lived experience, years of training and depth of study with intuitive adeptness and precise energetic attunement in her work. 

Tracy's soul mentorship is focused on midwifing souls into embodied depth and well being.  Her one on one practice welcomes individuals and couples and covers the following:
-Emotional fluency
-Nervous system regulation and stabilization
-Neuroplasticity training
-Relational wellness
-Erotic embodiment
-Practical integration for soulful living
-Clearing patterns and behaviors that inhibit wellness and radiance

Tracy's group work focuses on supporting fields of vibratory coherence between humans and building group capacity for generative healing , creativity, and collaboration. This work is deeply supportive for organizations, collectives, and any group wanting to understand relational dynamics to support generative and resourcing environments. Reach out directly to find out more about group work.3:["$","$L6",null,{"islandSlug":"big-island","islandDisplayName":"Big Island","modalitySlug":"nature-therapy","modalityName":"Nature Therapy","practitioners":[{"id":"e6b9190b-3712-4822-a948-eb68658ff6f7","name":"Upcoming Offerings","businessName":"Wild Women Hawai'i LLC","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4bf6fb_269e2ecdc5a04812a4d3df12517ffe82~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_1108,h_732,al_c/4bf6fb_269e2ecdc5a04812a4d3df12517ffe82~mv2.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Somatic Therapy, Women's Health, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Somatic Therapy","Women's Health","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Women’s retreats, somatic therapy, and women’s gatherings in Hilo and across the Big Island. Wild Women Hawai'i hosts private women’s gatherings rooted in wellness and friendship.","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4f0201fe-fd88-4166-860b-5f2e3eff5106","name":"Michelle Wellman","businessName":"Woman Of Horses","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/754508_5959ad9afad5470f87d98a3218aef380%7Emv2_d_2300_1534_s_2.jpg/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/754508_5959ad9afad5470f87d98a3218aef380%7Emv2_d_2300_1534_s_2.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"\nEquine Assisted Therapy\n\nEAGALA certified and ready to offer equine assisted psychotherapy! The team approach of a Mental Health Professional, Equine Specialist and Equine herd sets the space for transitions to happen in those seeking therapy. This is a post modern method and is 100% on the ground. With my team we can offer solution oriented sessions to hold space for you to heal. Contact for more information or to schedule a session.","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.927062,"lng":-155.783519,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"b393f147-f777-4b4a-a091-74aa35e44fe7","name":"Robbi Nanni","businessName":"Waikōloa Stables","image":"https://www.waikoloa.org/editor_upload/Image/Waiko%CC%84loaVillageAssociation.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Therapeutic Horse Riding\n\nRobbi Nanni is a Professional Association of Therapeutic Horsemanship (PATH) certified riding instructor who provides riding lessons to students with cognitive and/or physical disabilities.  Horses are extremely therapeutic and can help individuals overcome anxiety, learn to walk, talk, and many other breakthroughs for the student.  Depending on the student’s level of riding or disability there are two volunteers in addition to the instructor per rider during the lesson.","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.927199,"lng":-155.782814,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"bfcf85e1-b297-4c1d-8f9b-5227180cc026","name":"Tracy Kelleher","title":"Soul Guide & Somatic Mentor","businessName":"Harmonic Soul","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/avatars/1772157858125_576zypk9lwd.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Soul Guidance, Energy Healing, Nervous System Regulation, Trauma-Informed Care, Breathwork, Life Coaching, Counseling, Meditation, Ritualist, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Soul Guidance","Energy Healing","Nervous System Regulation","Trauma-Informed Care","Breathwork","Life Coaching","Counseling","Meditation","Ritualist","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"both","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"$7","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.082831,"lng":-155.833008,"tier":"featured","externalBookingUrl":"https://tracy-kelleher.com/contact","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-06T00:49:14.005373+00:00","verified":false}],"centers":[{"id":"6ab46f74-df28-44ca-85e1-3643c901ee31","name":"Ahu Lani Sanctuary","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/59f766a3d74cff20ceed67e2/t/59f7713364265f16160dea86/1509388600254/spiral-logo.png?format=1500w","modality":"Yoga, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Yoga","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Paauhau","rating":5,"lat":20.013804,"lng":-155.441775,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Big Island Hawaii Yoga Retreat Center and Education Facility","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"db8606c1-5a61-4760-926e-eaea68b2746d","name":"Cherry Healing Center","image":"https://cherryhealingcenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Cherry-Healing-Center_-Web-Banner.png","modality":"Acupuncture, Massage, Nature Therapy, TCM (Traditional Chinese Medicine)","modalities":["Acupuncture","Massage","Nature Therapy","TCM (Traditional Chinese Medicine)"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.72498,"lng":-155.089869,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"This is why we utilize a variety of therapeutic modalities such as acupuncture, massage, simple structural guidance, herbal formulas, and access to fresh nutritional foods to stimulate your body’s inherent ability to repair and restore vitality. ","centerType":"wellness_center","centerType