,"Sound Healing","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.705777,"lng":-155.947417,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Journey into the Mystical Kona Cloud Forest Sanctuary - Encounter Rare Species, Lush Greenery, and Peaceful Retreats. Find Your Paradise Today!","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"28e7f4f1-2caf-4766-bc78-4cfef8c90e6e","name":"Muaisa Hale Pule","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/centers/1774581196622-4yd8ujey4tx.webp","modality":"Energy Healing, Counseling, Meditation, Alternative Therapy, Soul Guidance, Art Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Energy Healing","Counseling","Meditation","Alternative Therapy","Soul Guidance","Art Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Captain Cook","rating":5,"lat":19.518149,"lng":-155.920678,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Muaisa Hale Pule's principal aim is its spiritually-focused programs, sessions and retreats. Whether you're kama'aima (an island resident) or you're visiting from off-island, we offer donor-funded guidance, direction, retreats, vision quests, and natural healing venues to support inner needs and assist with spiritual housekeeping.\n\n* * * * * 5.0\n\"My husband and i got all we needed and more. ZZ and Jack are absolutely the BEST. Their expertise spans far greater than you can imagine.\" \n--DM, 2022","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/centers/1774581196622-4yd8ujey4tx.webp"],"workingHours":{"fri":null,"mon":null,"sat":null,"sun":null,"thu":null,"tue":null,"wed":null},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"5c956014-a82c-4